About Me

 

 

Hi, my name is Clark Ryan M. Magalso, 19yrs old and was born on February 07, 2006. I live in Maria Cristina, Iligan City. I have two siblings and I am the eldest. When I was seven (7) years old, I used to play basketball because I was inspired by my father. I love cleaning house hold chores, like washing dishes, sweeping and mopping the floor.

 

I graduated high school at Our Lady of Perpetual Help Academy at Linamon, Kauswagan, Lanao del norte. Now, I am a college student and currently studying at MSU-IIT.

 

My hobbies are, playing basketball, listening to music, jogging, hiking, mountain climbing, swimming and I love eating fruits and vegetables to keep my body healthy.

 

My goals in life are, to be a successful businessman someday and to make my parents and my future wife proud, stable job and financially stable.

My favorite quote is, Focus on resilience, teamwork, self belief and hard work
